# Domain Logic & Rules (Invariant)

## Speech-to-Text (STT)

- **Rule**: STT outputs must be post-processed for veterinary context
- **Implementation**: Use `features/speech/services/sttService.ts`
- **Examples**: "Udder" > "Other"; "Creatinine" > "Creating"

## Time Progression

- **Rule**: Time is not linear; it is event-based (`CaseTimepoint`)
- **Enforcement**: Updating time requires explicitly updating the AI context (System Prompt) to match the new CaseTimepoint
